Package net.asrex.skillful.exception

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    EffectActivationException
    An exception thrown when an effect cannot be activated.
    EffectException
    An exception thrown when some precondition of high-level functionality relating to Effect instances is failed.
    PerkActivationException
    An exception thrown when perk activation fails.
    PerkException
    An exception thrown when some aspect of high-level Perk functionality fails to meet a precondition.
    SkillfulException
    An exception thrown when a generic, high-level error occurs in some part of Skillful core functionality.
